<DATELINE>
   ALGIERS
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
ALGERIA'S Foreign Ministry said yesterday that there was no truth in British
press reports that Iraq had supplied either experts or nuclear materials to
help Algeria build a military nuclear reactor.
Algeria said it had decided to submit both its nuclear reactors - at Draria
and at Ain Oussera - to the control of the International Atomic Energy
